metadata.name: The Anonymous NFT #1
metadata.description: Anonymous is here to help web3 users on how to detect, expose and report scams like never before. Holders will be able to claim a Free Anonymous Pass, which will allow them to access private alphas and be eligible for future claims. We are building a platform in our website, where users can have their own profile, interact with each other, share knowledge and learn more about web3. Our focus is to share awareness and to expose the truth. We are Legion. Expect Us.
